                        <persName key="person_f752">Buzurjumīd</persName>leading the funeral procession accompanied by water-sprinklers and men giving coins to bystanders.<locus n="95v"/>
                     </decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="miniature">
                        <locus n="96r"/>
                        <persName key="person_f4038">Shīrīn</persName>commiting suicide on<persName key="person_n84045832">Khusrau</persName>'s tomb.</decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="miniature">
                        <locus n="99r"/>
                        <persName key="person_n80115655" role="author">Niẓāmī</persName>presenting his poem "<persName key="person_n84045832">Khusrau</persName>u<persName key="person_f4038">Shīrīn</persName>" to one of the sons (either<persName key="person_f2903">Muḥammad</persName>or<persName key="person_f5524">Ḳizil Arslān</persName>) of<persName key="person_f1572">Ildigiz</persName>.</decoNote>
